snippet.title: Hockey - (1976) - Channel F - gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Hockey © 1976 - Fairchild Semiconductor
Fairchild Channel F console game (BIOS - included)

This is a review and playthrough of one of the two included games in the Fairchild Channel F console BIOS.  Not a bad pong clone.  The rotating paddle adds a nice new twist (har har).   -Videogame documentation project.
